  "text": "GameSpot may receive revenue from affiliate and advertising partnerships for sharing this content and from purchases through links. D\u0026D fans can save big on a really cool special-edition book box set at Amazon during the retailer's Big Spring Sale. Dungeons \u0026 Dragons Art \u0026 Arcana: A Visual History Special Edition is available for only $45.91 (was $125). To get the full $80 discount, you need to click the coupon box beneath the price on the store page to slash an additional $21.26 from the price. select the coupon box under the price listed on the book's Amazon store page. D\u0026D: Art \u0026 Arcana: A Visual History Special Edition Box Set $45.91 (was $125) Dungeons \u0026 Dragons Art \u0026 Arcana: A Visual History is a 448-page art book detailing the artistic evolution of the tabletop RPG. It includes concept sketches, official illustrations, photographs, and other material from D\u0026D's many rulebooks, adventure modules, novels, magazines, and more.The Special Edition includes an eye-catching display box with exclusive artwork. Inside the book-like box, you'll find the actual hardcover as well as 10 art prints, and a pamphlet of D\u0026D co-creator Gary Gygax's classic Tomb of Horrors adventure module, all within a clamshell case featuring original designs by D\u0026D artist Hydro74. Dungeons \u0026 Dragons: Art \u0026 Arcana: A Visual History Special EditionIt's worth noting that the standard hardcover edition of Dungeons \u0026 Dragons Art \u0026 Arcana: A Visual History is on sale for $26 (was $50) and eligible for Amazon's Buy Two, Get One Free Book Sale this week.Wizards of the Coast recently released an updated Monster Manual for D\u0026D's tabletop game. The Monster Manual joined the updated Player's Handbook and Dungeon Master's Guide, both of which received new editions for the first time in a decade.2024 Player's Handbook -- $45 ($50)2024 Dungeon Master's Guide -- $47 ($50)2024 Monster Manual -- $46 ($50)2024 Character Sheets -- $152024 Dungeon Master's Screen -- $19.39 Dungeons \u0026 Dragons fans should also check out the new Dragonlance Chronicles Omnibus, which Amazon just restocked after selling out at launch in February. It also happens to be discounted to $28 (was $35). Dragonlance Chronicles is a 1,000-plus page hardcover book compiling the first three books in the beloved fantasy series set in the world of D\u0026D. Fans should also consider The World of Dragonlance Book Bundle at Humble, which lets you get 26 novels for only $18.For more fantasy book deals, take a look at our roundups of Brandon Sanderson and Robert Jordan novels that are featured in Amazon's B2G1 Free Book Sale. James Bond Sean Connery 4K Steelbook Collection Is Up For Preorder Star Wars Skywalker Saga 4K Box Set Featured In Amazon's Spring Sale 8BitDo Ultimate 2 Controller Gets Nice Discount A Month After Its Release + Show More More Gaming, Tech, and Entertainment Deals \u0026 Preorders Links (5) Best 4K Blu-Rays \u0026 Box Sets In Amazon's B2G1 Free Big Spring Sale Lenovo Legion Go SteamOS Handheld Preorders Are Live At Best Buy Zelda: Twilight Princess 11-Book Manga Box Set Is Nearly 50% Off At Amazon Lego Transformers Optimus Prime Is Finally Back In Stock With A Big Discount Middle-earth 6-Film 4K Blu-Ray Collection Gets Huge Launch Discount Got a news tip or want to contact us directly? Email news@gamespot.com",
